  "description": "🔐 An SSL library for configuring http client or server. Rich with features such as hot reloading ssl and trusting additional certificates during runtime, combining multiple keystores, loading pem files and os/jdk certificates, logging certificate information during ssl handshake, bypassing ssl configuration from other libraries and more",
